= 2004-05-28 Wuermeling Party Top Candidate Criticises Council Decision =
--> [[Posselt040528De| deutsch]], [[Wuermeling040519En| Wuermeling 2004-05-19]], [[SwpatcninoEn| news]]
----

Bernd Posselt, a well-known politician and top candidate of the Christian Social Union for the European Parliament, the party of EP shadow rapporteur [[SwpatjwuermelingEn| Joachim Wuermeling]],
mentioned "boiling popular sentiment on software patents", expressed in hundreds of letters which he
has received, and promised to vote against the Council decision.

See [[Posselt020528De| german version]] for details.
